data.title: Evertons Cahill ties the knot with childhood sweetheart
data.meta_description: Everton and Australia star Tim Cahill has married his long-time partner Rebekah Greenhill in a ceremony in Las Vegas on the weekend. The 30-year old and his childhood sweetheart, also 30, tied the knot on their way to Sydney for Cahills World Cup preparations...
data.text: Everton and Australia star Tim Cahill has married his long-time partner Rebekah Greenhill in a ceremony in Las Vegas on the weekend. The 30-year old and his childhood sweetheart, also 30, tied the knot on their way to Sydney for Cahills World Cup preparations. The couple have three children, sons Kyah, 7, Shae, 5, and daughter Sienna, 3, who were all present and participated in the ceremony. Cahill and his new wife will land in Sydney today and attend a fundraising dinner reception gala tonight in aid of the Tim Cahill Cancer Fund for Children. For all the latest football news go to tribalfootball.com.
